OL,3,CAlmost 30,000 runners take on Cardiff
OL,4,CHalf Marathon 2024
OL,6,FAlmost 30,000 runners hit the streets
OL,7,Fof Cardiff on Sunday for the city's
OL,8,Fannual half marathon.
OL,10,FKenyan Patrick Mosin took the win with
OL,11,Fa time of 1:01.
OL,13,FParticipants were given a boost at
OL,14,Fmile 10 where Pride Cymru hosted the
OL,15,FPrincipality Rainbow Roundabout for a
OL,16,Fsecond year running.
OL,18,FDan Walsh, chair of Pride Cymru, said:
OL,19,F"The whole idea is to give a lift to
OL,20,Fthe runners as they enter a really
OL,21,Ftricky part of the course.
