OL,3,CAlmost 30,000 runners take on Cardiff
OL,4,CHalf Marathon 2024
OL,6,F"But it's also about showing the LGBT
OL,7,Fcommunity that you can be sporty.
OL,9,F"An international survey done a couple
OL,10,Fof years ago showed that 80% of LGBT
OL,11,Fpeople had experienced homophobia in
OL,12,Fsport, so it's really important we're
OL,13,Fhere to show that visibility for our
OL,14,Fcommunity."
OL,16,FAfter starting outside the castle,
OL,17,Frunners passed the Principality and
OL,18,FCardiff City Stadiums. They then
OL,19,Fprogressed onto Penarth and into the
OL,20,Fmarina, before crossing the barrage
OL,21,Fand heading into Cardiff Bay.
