OL,6,FThe course then headed towards the
OL,7,Fnorth of the city where runners
OL,8,Fcompleted a loop of Roath Park Lake.
OL,10,FAfter passing Roath Park, runners then
OL,11,Fheaded to the finish line outside the
OL,12,FCivic Centre on King Edward VII Avenue.
OL,14,FThe first Cardiff Half Marathon took
OL,15,Fplace in 2003 with 1,500 runners
OL,16,Ftaking part.
OL,18,FIt has now become part of the
OL,19,FSuperHalfs - a global series of the
OL,20,Fworld's most prestigious half
OL,21,Fmarathons.
